# Migration output: regenerated by scripts/migrate-v1-skills.
# Source of truth lives in scaffolds/ and v1's .claude/skills/.
/migration-output/

# Example projects: keep the framework setup + sample PRDs tracked,
# but ignore everything the CLI regenerates on init/sync/install/run.
# `samuel doctor --fix` and a fresh `samuel install …` reproduce all
# of these from the tracked samuel.toml + samuel.lock-less state.
examples/*/CLAUDE.md
examples/*/samuel.lock
examples/*/.samuel/lock
examples/*/.samuel/builtins/
examples/*/.samuel/plugins/
examples/*/.samuel/run/
